    {
      "id": "edge-contract-root",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Overview",
      "position": {
        "x": -980,
        "y": -120
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Edge Contract\n\n**Authority:** Normative\n\nThis contract defines the durable stored shape for Twilite edges. It governs endpoint identity, optional metadata, class assignment, validation, mutation policy, and transport portability.\n\nPlain edges remain valid without classes. Edge classes are the canonical semantic upgrade path.\n\nThis graph is the contract.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
