    {
      "id": "edge-meta",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "0. Metadata",
      "position": {
        "x": -380,
        "y": -120
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Metadata\n\n- Contract ID: edge-contract\n- Version: MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH\n- Status: experimental | stable | deprecated\n- Scope: all persisted edges\n- Defined in: `public/library/documentation/contracts/edges/edge-contract.node`\n- Notes: renderer fallbacks may tolerate missing endpoint metadata during migration, but persisted graph data should prefer the canonical stored shape described here",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
