    {
      "id": "edge-class-assignment",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "4b. Edge Class Assignment",
      "position": {
        "x": 120,
        "y": 260
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Edge Class Assignment (REQUIRED WHEN CLASSIFIED)\n\nA plain edge remains fully valid without a class.\n\nWhen an edge is classified, the canonical structure is:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"edgeClassRef\": \"github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/edges/task-depends-on.edge-class.node\",\n    \"edgeClassKey\": \"task.depends-on\",\n    \"edgeClassMeaning\": \"target must happen before source can complete\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\nRules:\n- `data.edgeClassRef` is the authoritative class reference moving forward\n- `data.edgeClassKey` is the stable human/search key and should match the referenced class when both are present\n- `data.edgeClassMeaning` is mirrored display metadata only; it is not the semantic authority\n- the edge-class artifact's **Field nodes** own `meaning`, `defaultEdgeType`, and `renderDefaults` (node-first contract)\n- instance `style`, `label`, and explicit `type` may override class defaults\n- if neither instance `type` nor class `defaultEdgeType` is present, the renderer falls back to a plain line\n\nMigration note:\n- legacy graphs may still carry `edgeClassKey` without `edgeClassRef`\n- readers should tolerate that during migration\n- new authored structures should prefer storing both",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
            "source": "local",
            "version": ">=0.1.0"
          },
          "views": [
            {
              "key": "markdown",
              "intent": "editor",
              "payload": "editor.web",
              "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
              "source": "local",
              "version": ">=0.1.0"
