    {
      "id": "edge-forbidden",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "5. Forbidden States",
      "position": {
        "x": 660,
        "y": 260
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Forbidden States (HARD ERROR)\n\nEdges must never:\n- reference missing nodes\n- reuse an existing edge id\n- invent non-existent ports\n- violate port contracts\n- contradict manifest authority\n- carry `edgeClassRef` that points at a missing edge-class artifact\n- carry both `edgeClassRef` and `edgeClassKey` with mismatched class identity",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
