    {
      "id": "edge-validation",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "6. Validation Rules",
      "position": {
        "x": 1120,
        "y": 260
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Validation Rules (REQUIRED)\n\nValidators MUST enforce:\n\n1. `id`, `source`, and `target` exist\n2. source and target exist\n3. persisted edges carry `sourcePort` and `targetPort`, or a loader explicitly normalizes omission before persistence\n4. provided endpoints satisfy node port or handle contracts\n5. if `type` exists, it is a string\n6. if `edgeClassRef` exists, the referenced edge-class artifact exists\n7. if both `edgeClassRef` and `edgeClassKey` exist, they agree\n8. manifest allows mutation\n\nFailure blocks persistence.\n\nMigration tolerance is allowed during load, import, or repair flows, but the saved graph should converge to explicit endpoint ids.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
            "source": "local",
            "version": ">=0.1.0"
