    {
      "id": "edge-mutations",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "7. Allowed Mutations",
      "position": {
        "x": -220,
        "y": 700
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Allowed Mutations\n\n- add edge: allowed\n- remove edge: allowed (unless appendOnly)\n- add, remove, or change runtime `type`: allowed if compatible\n- assign or remove edge class: allowed\n- update instance style overrides: allowed\n- update instance label, state, routing, or extensions: allowed\n- rewire edge endpoints: platform-capable, but discouraged as a durable authoring policy\n\nAuthoring policy:\n- prefer delete + recreate over silent rewiring when relationship identity changes\n- only preserve edge identity across endpoint changes when the workflow is explicitly performing a retarget operation\n\nMutations not listed remain undefined and should be treated cautiously.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
