    {
      "id": "edge-portability",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "9. Portability Guarantee",
      "position": {
        "x": 900,
        "y": 700
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Portability Guarantee\n\nEdges remain portable when:\n- endpoint ids are explicit, especially explicit `root`\n- styles are ignored\n- editors differ\n- renderers change\n- class defaults are unavailable and only instance data remains\n\nLegacy omission of endpoint ids may still be repairable in tolerant readers, but explicit endpoint storage is the durable transport shape.\n\nMeaning must survive transport.\n\nWhere possible, carry both `edgeClassRef` and `edgeClassKey` so transport can preserve both durable authority and lightweight local discoverability.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
